headline: 2 No-Brainer High-Yield Dividend Growth Stocks to Buy With $500 Right Now
summary: When investors think about high-yield stocks, the yield is often the only issue considered.  Right now, dividend investors should probably be considering reliable income stocks like Enterprise Products Partners (NYSE: EPD) and United Parcel Service (NYSE: UPS).  Enterprise Products Partners is a master limited partnership (MLP) that operates in the midstream segment of the oil and natural gas industry.
